- **GET /api/notifications/pending**  
  **What it does:** Returns pending notification queue items for Make/worker (`limit` query param, 1..20).  
  **Call:**
  ```powershell
  $secret="make_notify_key_here"

  Invoke-RestMethod `
    -Method Get `
    -Uri "http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/pending?limit=10" `
    -Headers @{ "x-api-key"=$secret }
  ```

- **POST /api/notifications/ack**  
  **What it does:** Marks one notification queue item as sent (acknowledgement endpoint).  
  **Call:**
  ```powershell
  $secret="make_notify_key_here"
  $body = @{ id="<notification_queue_id>" } | ConvertTo-Json

  Invoke-RestMethod `
    -Method Post `
    -Uri "http://localhost:3000/api/notifications/ack" `
    -Headers @{ "x-api-key"=$secret } `
    -ContentType "application/json" `
    -Body $body
  ```

- **POST /api/notify/make/pull**  
  **What it does:** Legacy-style pull endpoint for Make; fetches pending queue items (`limit` in JSON body, max 50).  
  **Call:**
  ```powershell
  $secret="make_notify_key_here"
  $body = @{ limit=20 } | ConvertTo-Json

  Invoke-RestMethod `
    -Method Post `
    -Uri "http://localhost:3000/api/notify/make/pull" `
    -Headers @{ "x-api-key"=$secret } `
    -ContentType "application/json" `
    -Body $body
  ```

- **POST /api/notify/make/ack**  
  **What it does:** Legacy-style ack endpoint for Make; sets queue item status to `sent` or `failed` and increments attempts.  
  **Call:**
  ```powershell
  $secret="make_notify_key_here"
  $body = @{ id="<notification_queue_id>"; status="sent" } | ConvertTo-Json

  Invoke-RestMethod `
    -Method Post `
    -Uri "http://localhost:3000/api/notify/make/ack" `
    -Headers @{ "x-api-key"=$secret } `
    -ContentType "application/json" `
    -Body $body
  ```

- **POST /api/missions/ingest**  
  **What it does:** Protected ingest endpoint to insert one mission for a user email (requires active/trialing subscription, includes rate limit).  
  **Call:**
  ```powershell
  $secret="make_ingest_key_here"
  $body = @{
    userEmail = "you@example.com"
    mission = @{
      source = "malt"
      title = "Senior Next.js Contractor"
      company = "Acme"
      country = "France"
      remote = "remote"
      dayRate = 800
      url = "https://example.com/job/123"
      score = 86
      reasons = "Strong stack match and remote preference"
      pitch = "I can help build and optimize your Next.js platform..."
    }
  } | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 6

  Invoke-RestMethod `
    -Method Post `
    -Uri "http://localhost:3000/api/missions/ingest" `
    -Headers @{ "x-api-key"=$secret } `
    -ContentType "application/json" `
    -Body $body
  ```
